name: Invesco S&P US Total Market ESG Index ETF
longDescription: Invesco S&P US Total Market ESG Index ETF the ETF seeks replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the S&P Composite 1500 ESG Index the underlying index or any successor thereto, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units. This Invesco ETF invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in equity securities of companies listed in the United States.
